, 64, 64); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">So why =
the big push for U.S. manufacturing?</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64);=
 font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">On the public sid=
e, The Biden Administration has declared the production of electric vehicle=
s, semiconductors, and other goods a matter of national security. And the A=
dministration has pumped tens of billions into onshoring the capacity and t=
alent needed to build those goods in the U.S.</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(64,=
 64, 64); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;"><span>On=
 the private side, companies learned during the early days of the pandemic =
that their fragile supply chains were a bit over reliant on China and could=
